            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:6;65:16" xtrf="file:/Users/joe.zucker/git/examples/source/dita-spec-1-3/introduction/formatting-conventions-xhtml-output.dita">The following screen capture illustrates how navigation links are displayed in the
